and Build Tools (npm, yarn, grunt);</li>\n<li>Git;</li>\n<li>Python;</li>\n<li>Python Tools (pip, pyenv, virtualenv, pipenv, fabric)</li>\n<li>Python Web Frameworks (Django, Flask, Chalice);</li>\n<li>Python Data Analysis &#x26; AI Libraries (Numpy, Pandas, Scikit.learn);</li>\n<li>Docker;</li>\n<li>Other programming Languages: Java, Ruby, R, C</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Contacts</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Mail</strong>: giuseppe [at] rightright [dot] me.</li>\n<li><strong>Twitter</strong>: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/glsorre\" target=\"_blank\">@glsorre</a></li>\n<li><strong>Linkedin</strong>: <a href=\"https://it.linkedin.com/in/glsorrentino\" target=\"_blank\">Giuseppe Sorrentino</a></li>\n<li><strong>Github</strong>: <a href=\"https://github.com/glsorre\" target=\"_blank\">@glsorre</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":null,"path":"/aboutme","title":"about me"}}},"pageContext":{}}